name: Aux Armes Et Caetera
wikiSummary: This is Serge Gainsbourg recording in Jamaica in 1978. The song "Aux Armes et cetera", is a reggae version of the French national anthem "La Marseillaise", with Jamaicans Robbie Shakespeare, Sly Dunbar, and Rita Marley (wife of Bob).
wikiText:
This is Serge Gainsbourg recording in Jamaica in 1978. The song "Aux Armes et cetera", is a reggae version of the French national anthem "La Marseillaise", with Jamaicans Robbie Shakespeare, Sly Dunbar, and Rita Marley (wife of Bob).
